Text: Status of your ETRADE AccountETRADE Customer We have received your new account application and if all the information is in good order your account will be opened and activated within two business days If we have questions regarding your application well call you at the phone number you provided You applied for your account online and preselected a User Name and Password Heres how to check to see if your account is activated using your preselected User Name and Password Click the Log On button of the ETRADE home page at Click on the Log On button in Yellow Enter your preselected User Name and Password Click on the Account Services tab on the top navigation bar If you see a message saying this is a customeronly feature then your account has not yet been activated If the Account Services section loads your account is activated and you can now access all the customeronly features of the ETRADE Web site Please note You can start placing trades as soon as your initial deposit clears or assets from a transfer have been received by ETRADE When you place a trade you will be asked for your Trading PasswordThis is the same password as your LogOn Password Youll receive a Welcome Kit from us in the mail within seven business days after we activate your account This package contains important information about your account including all your access codes and a handy users manual our clickbyclick guide to online investing If you do not receive your Welcome Kit within ten business days please send a customer service email request by clicking theCustomer Support support on the home page or go to customersupporthtml If your account is not yet activated you can still use ETRADEs Web site to access useful information such as ESTATION ETRADEs hour assistance center ESTATION contains an online Tour that allows you to navigate the site and learn about its powerful features a Learning Center where you can find useful information and answers to your investing and account questions and a Service Center where you can send us electronic service requests To visit ESTATION click on the Customer Support button on the ETRADE home page or go to customersupporthtml We hope you enjoy and profit from your relationship with ETRADE and we look forward to serving your financial needs for many years to come Sincerely ETRADE Customer Service The services described herein are available to US residents only Copyright c ETRADER Securities Inc Member NASDSIPC All rights reserved

Status of your ETRADE AccountAfter you read this email remember to check out your ETRADE Online Welcome Kit at welcome Dear ETRADE Customer Congratulations Youve taken your first step on the road to financial freedom and opened an ETRADE investment account Now its time to take the next steps Follow the instructions below to access your Online Welcome Kit where you can easily explore the wide range of resources available to you as an ETRADE customer Go to welcome Click the yellow Get Started button Enter your preselected User Name and Password Click the Log On button We hope you enjoy and profit from your relationship with ETRADE We look forward to serving your financial needs for many years to come Sincerely Suzi White Vice President Service Quality PS When youre ready to place your first trade you will be asked for your Trading Password This is the same password as your Log On Password You may change either password at any time by clicking the Set Passwords Features link under the Account Services tab System response and account access times may vary due to a variety of factors including trading volumes market conditions system performance and other factors The services described herein are available to US residents only Copyright ETRADE Securities Inc All rights reserved Member NASDSIPC All trademarks and registered trademarks mentioned herein are the property of ETRADE Group Inc or its subsidiaries
